# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Agentic RAG System — Environment Configuration
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values.
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── LLM Provider ──────────────────────────────────────
# Which LLM provider to use for generation.
# Options: "gemini" or "groq"
LLM_PROVIDER=gemini

# ── API Keys ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Google Gemini API key.
# Get yours at: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# Groq API key (required only if LLM_PROVIDER=groq).
# Get yours at: https://console.groq.com/keys
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here

# Tavily API key for web search augmentation.
# Get yours at: https://app.tavily.com/home
TAVILY_API_KEY=your_tavily_api_key_here

# ── Storage Paths ─────────────────────────────────────
# Path where ChromaDB persists its vector store.
CHROMA_DB_PATH=./chroma_data

# Path to the SQLite database file for metadata/traces.
SQLITE_DB_PATH=./agentic_rag.db

# ── Model Configuration ──────────────────────────────
# HuggingFace embedding model used for vector embeddings.
# Default: all-MiniLM-L6-v2 (fast, 384-dim)
EMBEDDING_MODEL=all-MiniLM-L6-v2

# Cross-encoder model used for reranking retrieved chunks.
# Default: cross-encoder/ms-marco-MiniLM-L-6-v2
RERANKER_MODEL=cross-encoder/ms-marco-MiniLM-L-6-v2

# ── Feature Toggles ──────────────────────────────────
# Enable web search as a fallback when local retrieval is insufficient.
# Options: true / false
ENABLE_WEB_SEARCH=true

# Enable LLM-based fallback when the primary answer fails validation.
# Options: true / false
ENABLE_LLM_FALLBACK=true

# ── Retry Limits ──────────────────────────────────────
# Maximum number of retrieval retries before escalating to fallback.
MAX_RETRIEVAL_RETRIES=3

# Maximum number of generation retries for hallucination correction.
MAX_GENERATION_RETRIES=2

# ── Thresholds ────────────────────────────────────────
# Hallucination score threshold (0.0–1.0).
# Answers scoring above this are flagged and regenerated.
HALLUCINATION_THRESHOLD=0.2

# Minimum confidence required for the query router to commit to a strategy.
# Below this, the system uses a default or multi-strategy approach.
ROUTING_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD=0.7

# ── Retrieval Settings ────────────────────────────────
# Number of chunks to retrieve in the initial broad retrieval pass.
TOP_K_RETRIEVAL=20

# Number of chunks to keep after reranking for final answer generation.
TOP_K_FINAL=5
